_sText:
Note: I did not make this map, I am just re-distributing it.
Changes Made from Original
  • Kitchen Area layout different
  • Restaurant eating area updated. (nicer booths, and tables)
  • Side door to kitchen added on side of ordering area.
  • Double Door fixed (no longer spins)
  • Bathrooms look nicer
  • Imported car models (no longer crappy hl2 broken car prop)
Almost forgot to mention mds asked me for the ip of my server after he gave me this updated version. Since I not longer run any game servers I was not able to give him an ip to a server for him to play on. If any of you guys make a server that runs this map, please let me know so I can forward it to mds so he can play on your server.
Install the map into your/server cstrike/map folder.
Fraps Test - mcdonalds-mds-v2-beta
